FBIS3-14980 "drsov041_g_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-041 Document Type:Daily Report 2 Mar 1994 WESTERN REGION Belarus Hryb Urges Economic Union With Russia WS0203103094 Minsk Radio Minsk Network in Belarusian 0400 GMT 2 Mar 94 WS0203103094 Minsk Radio Minsk Network Language: Belarusian Article Type:BFN [Text] Mechyslaw Hryb, new speaker of the Belarusian parliament, has spoken in favor of urgently reestablishing economic ties with former republics of the USSR, in particular, with Russia. In an interview with Moscow PRAVDA, he said that the only way out of the crisis for Belarus leads through an economic union and a single monetary system with Russia.
